          "text": "SBMR",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", to provide a comprehensive view of both active and historical account and meter information. The procedure returns a result set that includes details such as meter numbers, account numbers, facility identifiers, and activity status."
        }
